{"lemma":"مَراضَى","slug":"مَراضَى","root":"م.ر.ض","root_slug":"م-ر-ض","root_link":"/words/roots/م-ر-ض","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"مَرِيض","root":"مرض","pos":"N","occurrence_count":10},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["adj","noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":3},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n38488"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%85%D9%8E%D8%B1%D8%A7%D8%B6%D9%8E%D9%89"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"adj","gloss":"sick, ill (in poor health)","examples":[{"text":"الصِّحَّةُ تَاجٌ عَلَى رُؤُوسِ الْأَصِحَّاءِ لَا يَرَاهُ إِلَّا الْمَرْضَى.","english":"Health is a crown on the heads of the healthy, that only the ill can see."},{"text":"یۡسَ عَلَى ٱلۡأَعۡمَىٰ حَرَجࣱ وَلَا عَلَى ٱلۡأَعۡرَجِ حَرَجࣱ وَلَا عَلَى ٱلۡمَرِیضِ حَرَجࣱۗ وَمَن یُطِعِ ٱللَّهَ وَرَسُولَهُۥ یُدۡخِلۡهُ جَنَّـٰتࣲ تَجۡرِی مِن تَحۡتِهَا ٱلۡأَنۡهَـٰرُۖ وَمَن یَتَوَلَّ یُعَذِّبۡهُ عَذَابًا أَلِیمࣰا.","english":"There is no blame for the blind, nor is there the blame for the lame, nor is there blame for the sick (that they go not forth to war). And whoso obeyeth Allah and His messenger, He will make him enter Gardens underneath which rivers flow; and whoso turneth back, him will He punish with a painful doom."}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"patient (ill person; person who receives treatment from a doctor)"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"psychopath"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"فَعِيل (faʕīl)-type stative-verb derived from the active participle from the verb مَرِضَ (mariḍa, “to become sick”)."},"ipa":["/ma.riːdˤ/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n38488","headword_ar":"مَرِيضٌ","root":"mrD","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Diseased; disordered; distempered; sick;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ill;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the state termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maraDN","text_ar":"مَرَضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, K) denoting that change of the constitution or temperament which is described in the explanation of the latter word above; (K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mariDN","text_ar":"مَرِضٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maAriDN","text_ar":"مَارِضٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (IB, Msb, K,) the first [and second] being from the verb of which the inf. n. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maraDN","text_ar":"مَرَضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and the third from that of which the inf. n. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maroDN","text_ar":"مَرْضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mamoruwDN","text_ar":"مَمْرُوضٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mutamar~iDN","text_ar":"مُتَمَرِّضٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) or, applied to a body, it signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"deficient in strength:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"miraADN","text_ar":"مِرَاضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, K, TA:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maroDaY","text_ar":"مَرْضَى"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IDrd, Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maraADaY","text_ar":"مَرَاضَى"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IDrd, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muraDaA='u","text_ar":"مُرَضَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"miraADN","text_ar":"مِرَاضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"may be pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maAriDN","text_ar":"مَارِضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA) [or of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mariDN","text_ar":"مَرِضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. Accord. to Lh, you say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eudo fulaAnN faA_in~ahu mariyDN","text_ar":"عُدْ فُلَانٌ فَاـِنَّهُ مَرِيضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Visit thou such a one, for he is sick"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA taA^okulo h`*aA","text_ar":"لَا تَاْكُلْ هٰذَا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ino A^akalotahu","text_ar":"اـِنْ اَكَلْتَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlT~aEaAma faA_in~aka maAriDN","text_ar":"الطَّعَامَ فَاـِنَّكَ مَارِضٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tamoraDu","text_ar":"تَمْرَضُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Eat not thou this food, for thou wilt be sick if thou eat it"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mariyDN","text_ar":"مَرِيضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"has also several tropical significations.] You say also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EayonN mariyDapN","text_ar":"عَيْنٌ مَرِيضَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An eye in which is languor,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"languidness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"weakness:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEoyanN miraADN","text_ar":"اَعْيَنٌ مِرَاضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maroDaY","text_ar":"مَرْضَى"},{"kind":"text","text":". (A, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_imoraA^apN mariyDapu AlA^aloHaAZi","text_ar":"اـِمْرَاَةٌ مَرِيضَةُ الاَلْحَاظِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mryDpu","text_ar":"مريضةُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aln~aZari","text_ar":"النَّظَرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A woman weak in sight."},{"kind":"text","text":"(IDrd.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qalobN mariyDN","text_ar":"قَلْبٌ مَرِيضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A heart deficient in religion."},{"kind":"text","text":"[IAar.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$amosN mariyDapN","text_ar":"شَمْسٌ مَرِيضَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A sun having a feeble light;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, K; *)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"not clear,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and not beautiful."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aroDN mariyDapN","text_ar":"اَرْضٌ مَرِيضَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A land in which are frequent seditions,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"factions,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"conflicts,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dissensions,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and wars,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and slaughters:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in a weak condition:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"straitened with its inhabitants:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in which the wind is still, and the heat intense:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that causes disease;"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"corrupt in its air."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riyHN mariyDapN","text_ar":"رِيحٌ مَرِيضَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, K) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A weak wind:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a still wind:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a wind intensely hot, and blowing feebly."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"layolapN mariyDapN","text_ar":"لَيْلَةٌ مَرِيضَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A night in which no star shines;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in which the sky is clouded, so that there is no light."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raA^oYN","text_ar":"رَاْىٌ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mariyDN","text_ar":"مَرِيضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An opinion deviating from what is right."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["Msb","K","IB","TA","IAar","A","IDrd","S"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}